dc_title_s: 1892 Plan of Lands Belonging to the Church of St. Francis of Assisium, Trenton, NJ
dc_description_s: A hand drawn survey map of the lands belonging to the Church of St Francis of Assisium, dated October 19, 1892. The map shows Front Street to Lafayette Street, from the property of Albert Winkler (next to parsonage) to the property belonging to the estate of John Hancock on Peace Street. The map includes the school house, the sisters' house, the church and the parsonage. Scale: 1 inch = 20 feet.
